@startuml authenticated-request-flow

title Authenticated Request — AT in Memory + Opaque Token Introspection

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 8

actor       "User"                           as user
participant "Angular"                        as spa   #LightGray
participant "Angular HTTP Interceptor"       as inter #LightGray
participant "BearerTokenAuthFilter"          as btf   #Orange
participant "KeycloakOpaqueTokenIntrospector" as intro #LightBlue
participant "Keycloak /introspect"           as kc    #LightGreen
participant "KeycloakOpaqueRoleConverter"    as conv  #LightBlue
participant "DpopAuthenticationFilter"       as dpop  #LightCoral
participant "Controller"                     as ctrl  #LightBlue
database    "Your DB (RBAC)"                 as db    #LightYellow

user  -> spa   : performs action
spa   -> inter : outgoing HTTP request

note over inter
  Interceptor attaches AT from memory:
  Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
end note

inter -> btf  : GET /api/clients\nAuthorization: Bearer <access_token>

btf   -> intro : introspect(token)
intro -> kc    : POST /introspect\nclient_id + client_secret + token

alt token active
    kc    --> intro : { active: true, sub, realm_access, resource_access, cnf.jkt }
    intro -> conv   : convert(attributes)
    conv  --> intro : [ROLE_user, ROLE_data_analyst, ...]
    intro --> btf   : OAuth2AuthenticatedPrincipal

    note over btf, dpop
      Filter chain order:
      TraceId → BearerTokenAuth → DPoP → RateLimit → Controller
    end note

    btf   -> dpop  : SecurityContext populated
    dpop  -> ctrl  : authenticated
    ctrl  -> db    : check permission('read:customers')
    db    --> ctrl : allowed
    ctrl  --> spa  : 200 OK + response body
    spa   --> user : renders data

else token expired (401)
    kc    --> intro : { active: false }
    intro --> btf   : OAuth2IntrospectionException
    btf   --> inter : 401 Unauthorized

    note over inter
      Interceptor catches 401.
      Triggers silent refresh before retrying.
      See: seq-refresh.puml
    end note

    inter --> spa  : retry with new AT or redirect to login
end

@enduml
